        \n<b>2.) Send Crime Details directly to police database</b>
        \nUser can use this option to directly send the crime details to police database
        \n<b>3.) View List of Reported Crimes</b>
        \nUser can use this option to view the list of Crimes he has reported so far.
        \n <b>4.) Delete a Crime</b>
        \nUser can use this option to delete a existing Crime in the list, by long pressing it.
        \n <b>4.) Get statistics</b>
        \nUser can use this option to get statistics from the police database.He can use it to see what are the various areas in which crimes have been reported so far.
        \n<b> 5.) Get Status of Crime</b>
        \n User can use this option to check that whether the crime he has reported is solved or not.

